title: 30. Stretch + Release Your Way to Contoured Skin: The Art + Science of Lymphatic Drainage With Michele Phelan
description:
Hi esties! We sat down with Michele Phelan to talk lymphatic drainage, aromatherapy, and the science of esthetics. Michele has been a licensed and practicing esthetician for 30 years. She owns her own private practice for 20+ years, and is an active educator for Concepts Institute in San Francisco, CA. All classes are online for the remainder of May 2020! 

Fine Michele and her courses at www.conceptsinstitute.com

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly

Music by LiQwYd
